40:30.710 --> 40:31.790
Yes, I'm fine.

40:31.790 --> 40:36.250
Um...just, uh, butterfly
caught me off guard.

40:36.250 --> 40:37.880
[ Chuckles nervously ]
So...

40:37.880 --> 40:40.170
I saw 'em when I was
traveling last summer.

40:40.170 --> 40:44.120
They're absolutely
radiant in person.

40:44.120 --> 40:45.750
[ Clears throat ]

