the big guns.

41:13.210 --> 41:15.460
[ Breathes deeply ]

41:15.460 --> 41:18.210
♪♪

41:18.210 --> 41:23.960
Oh. God is good, God is great,
and we thank Him for our food.

41:23.960 --> 41:25.960
Amen.

41:25.960 --> 41:27.620
[ Gasps ]

41:27.620 --> 41:30.420
